00:52:07,763 --> 00:52:09,363
Nakoniec som si to uvedomil.

667
00:52:09,933 --> 00:52:11,393
Čo je to?

668
00:52:11,993 --> 00:52:13,233
Povedz mi.

669
00:52:17,063 --> 00:52:21,063
